<i>noun</i>: 설복 [설복], 설득 [설뜩] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>설복 [설복]</dt><br>
<dd>persuasion</dd><br>
<dd>상대방이 알아듣도록 말하여 이해시키거나 그렇다고 인정하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a person understand or acknowledge a fact by explaining.</dd><br>
<dt>설득 [설뜩]</dt><br>
<dd>persuasion</dd><br>
<dd>상대방이 그 말을 따르거나 이해하도록 잘 설명하거나 타이름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of explaining or persuading so that a person would understand or do as asked.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>